EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
CANARY ISLANDS TO CAPE VERDE.
DNC 01.
30 FOOT S/V BAMBOU, GREY HULL WITH YELLOW STRIPE,
TWO PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE LA GOMERA (28-10N 017-21W)
TO CAPE VERDE (14-55N 023-31W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
